{"msg":{"practice":[{"id":190,"question":"老王凭借手艺开了一家修鞋店，但近年来找他修鞋的人越来越少、生意越来越差，老王很是苦恼。在儿子小王的建议下，他购进了设备，将修鞋店改成鞋子干洗、保养的店，生意又变得红火了。<br/><br/>小王的建议体现了SCAMPER中的哪些思维？","type":2,"analysis":"Substitute 用鞋子干洗、保养业务代替维修<br/>Adapt 适应了人们生活水平提高、修鞋需求变少、保养需求增加的现状","pic":null,"difficulty":3,"knowledgeId":15,"sceneId":1,"del":true,"problemId":3,"sequence":13,"example":false,"practiceUid":"T003C002F003X01013","score":50,"choiceList":[{"id":604,"questionId":190,"subject":"Substitute替代","sequence":1,"isRight":true,"selected":false},{"id":605,"questionId":190,"subject":"Combine合并","sequence":2,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":606,"questionId":190,"subject":"Adapt适应","sequence":3,"isRight":true,"selected":false},{"id":607,"questionId":190,"subject":"Modify修改","sequence":4,"isRight":false,"selected":false}],"discussList":[{"id":627,"warmupPracticeId":190,"repliedId":446,"comment":"同意，修改是要建立在原有的基础上的，修鞋店的服务原本是修鞋，而现在是干洗和保养，修鞋服务完全被替代了，修改也就没有基础了。","openid":null,"addTime":1488692013000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":"个人理解修改是针对产品或服务本身进行调整改动，但本题中，并没有提到对修鞋工艺或服务有什么改动，而且增加了服务品种。","del":0,"repliedName":"Yanae Yang","name":"大头娃娃","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoNEvKRFpbeOmYHJcFmkdv2hiaKchUpf7g590IA9HhXv7c4GmX8j4jP25LT0ATygpmZwibqTTOBtHta/0","discussTime":"2017-03-05"},{"id":616,"warmupPracticeId":190,"repliedId":399,"comment":"+1","openid":null,"addTime":1488629824000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":"为什么没有修改","del":0,"repliedName":"晓露sheri","name":"八戒","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQE8wJ7qQSJTlmaTJcTpaQUDoCs6iaFkricgianiaPnqibdWLBibGmu1of7mDBeXib5lVAkgQ6Z0MiaUG6WiaQ/0","discussTime":"2017-03-04"},{"id":446,"warmupPracticeId":190,"repliedId":399,"comment":"个人理解修改是针对产品或服务本身进行调整改动，但本题中，并没有提到对修鞋工艺或服务有什么改动，而且增加了服务品种。","openid":null,"addTime":1488355910000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":"为什么没有修改","del":0,"repliedName":"晓露sheri","name":"Yanae Yang","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98WUxgnmxEpgcwKia4vSaVZr6Oyx2wYIgoMAk7cUOb6WN5T3vPfq7c4AdwgTmtGH75t6NspLErm5UhaZIYRRg6oTH/0","discussTime":"2017-03-01"},{"id":399,"warmupPracticeId":190,"repliedId":null,"comment":"为什么没有修改","openid":null,"addTime":1488248266000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"晓露sheri","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyxPrKibibicpRzMx57Dib8I3mv4PIzcBzYNV8PZ3rMsjPExB3icliaYpuJL3KGBMEdqaAEPKN83ayRcnibO/0","discussTime":"2017-02-28"},{"id":288,"warmupPracticeId":190,"repliedId":117,"comment":"同问。","openid":null,"addTime":1487996396000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":"为什么没有修改，不是将服务的类型做了修改么？","del":0,"repliedName":"Lydia lv","name":"lanlan","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoABxary8VgXcewR1AmF19vgqh1yjicvfMjehwnN9BCtpicJfHXYmt3tEsP23v1u2lfVGIFicncrooia2/0","discussTime":"2017-02-25"},{"id":117,"warmupPracticeId":190,"repliedId":null,"comment":"为什么没有修改，不是将服务的类型做了修改么？","openid":null,"addTime":1487582327000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"Lydia lv","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoEafbGd5XibVcAc89Rp08bx9DygpIAwy1WZard9xTLrecFTjclgKZbleOMWAUZEdpBEQFS578kpdO/0","discussTime":"2017-02-20"}],"choice":null,"knowledge":{"id":15,"knowledge":"用SCAMPER结构化头脑风暴","step":"结构化思考","analysis":"SCAMPER（由七个英文单词或短语的首字母构成）是一种用于头脑风暴的问题清单，它为普通的头脑风暴提供了更为结构化的指导。通常适用于改进某个产品或服务的情景。","means":"在改进产品或服务时，用以下七个问题一一发问，拓展思路：\nSubstitute（代替）：成分、材料、人员是否有可替代方案，乃至对旧产品、旧服务可以进行替代吗？\nCombine（合并）：资源、品类、功能等是否存在合并的可能？\nAdapt（适应）：产品或服务能适应哪些其他场景？\nModify（修改）：产品的颜色、形状等特征可以作何修改？\nPut to other uses（作为他用）：产品或服务还有哪些新用途吗？\nEliminate（简化）：产品或服务可以做哪些简化？\nReverse（rearrange）（反向、重新安排）：产品或服务可以怎样逆向操作、重新安排？\n","keynote":"SCAMPER问题清单可以使你打开思路、拓展想法，但并非每个问题的答案都适合需要\n","pic":null,"audio":"http://www.iqycamp.com/audio/rise_k15.m4a","appear":0,"example":null}},{"id":192,"question":"笑话一则：<br/>李大爷买西红柿，挑了3个到秤盘，摊主秤了下：“一斤半3块7。”李大爷：“做汤不用那么多。”去掉了最大的西红柿。摊主，“一斤二两，3块。”<br/>正当我想提醒大爷注意秤子时，大爷从容的掏出了七毛钱，拿起刚刚去掉的那个大的西红柿，扭头就走。摊主当场无风凌乱。<br/><br/>李大爷的机智做法体现了SCAMPER中的哪种思维？","type":1,"analysis":"Reverse <br/>李大爷用逆向思维智斗无良小贩","pic":null,"difficulty":2,"knowledgeId":58,"sceneId":1,"del":false,"problemId":3,"sequence":2,"example":false,"practiceUid":"Z003T003C002D006X01002","score":30,"choiceList":[{"id":618,"questionId":192,"subject":"Eliminate消除","sequence":1,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":619,"questionId":192,"subject":"Reverse逆向","sequence":2,"isRight":true,"selected":false},{"id":620,"questionId":192,"subject":"Adapt适应","sequence":3,"isRight":false,"selected":false}],"discussList":[],"choice":null,"knowledge":{"id":58,"knowledge":"内容回顾 & 综合练习2","step":"复习","analysis":null,"means":null,"keynote":null,"pic":null,"audio":null,"appear":0,"example":null}},{"id":185,"question":"利用网页观看视频时，移动鼠标到窗口外，播放的菜单栏就会自动收起。<br/><br/>这种设计体现了SCAMPER中的哪种思维方式？","type":1,"analysis":"Eliminate 将原来的“移动-点击关闭”动作简化为“移动”","pic":null,"difficulty":2,"knowledgeId":57,"sceneId":1,"del":false,"problemId":3,"sequence":2,"example":false,"practiceUid":"Y003T003C002A002X01002","score":30,"choiceList":[{"id":573,"questionId":185,"subject":"Substitute替代","sequence":1,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":576,"questionId":185,"subject":"Modify修改","sequence":2,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":577,"questionId":185,"subject":"Put to other uses改作他用","sequence":3,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":578,"questionId":185,"subject":"Eliminate消除","sequence":4,"isRight":true,"selected":false}],"discussList":[{"id":626,"warmupPracticeId":185,"repliedId":258,"comment":"我的理解是修改只是把产品的某一或某些具体特征进行重新处理使其发生变化；而简化是把产品的某些特征去掉。就这道题而言，如果是修改的话，鼠标移出窗口和关闭菜单这两个步骤都要有，只是在这两个步骤上做了其它的处理。","openid":null,"addTime":1488691593000,"priority":1,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":"修改为啥不对？有些混淆修改与简化的区别了","del":0,"repliedName":"Jessie Wu\uD83C\uDF80\uD83D\uDC98","name":"大头娃娃","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoNEvKRFpbeOmYHJcFmkdv2hiaKchUpf7g590IA9HhXv7c4GmX8j4jP25LT0ATygpmZwibqTTOBtHta/0","discussTime":"2017-03-05"},{"id":1465,"warmupPracticeId":185,"repliedId":null,"comment":"修改我是这样理解的，之前可能是导航栏无论是鼠标在播放区域内还是外，都存在，现在改成鼠标移动到视频区域外就消失。这是改变形式或者动态的改变外观","openid":null,"addTime":1490670895000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"Peter","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoDcHxeWtQYv2UGlg2IxShJKu5E8JdibAXg9Ssfk8Wib8cLL3wZzbbIfIam8O1Va5ic5nOWKqjAElKzG/0","discussTime":"2017-03-28"},{"id":856,"warmupPracticeId":185,"repliedId":258,"comment":"可以多看下知识点中的举例说明，来理解题目中修改与简化等词的具体意思，而不要根据平时认为的词的意思来做题","openid":null,"addTime":1489492708000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":"修改为啥不对？有些混淆修改与简化的区别了","del":0,"repliedName":"Jessie Wu\uD83C\uDF80\uD83D\uDC98","name":"Chuan","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/TVwhicV1539IW2Fx75h6RibamKCK8uuoacbYS5yGavNuEssFugKg6UXLemfUj5nYtsNpFFZY3dOswIaakVONDeQswbqBDTcD32/0","discussTime":"2017-03-14"},{"id":268,"warmupPracticeId":185,"repliedId":null,"comment":"越来越迷糊了。第一，这个功能能不能给点图啊？我对移动鼠标-收起菜单栏没什么印象呢〒_〒\n第二，收起菜单栏是为了使用其他程序，是否可以理解为移做他用呢？","openid":null,"addTime":1487922063000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"郭舒简","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XRibESzncllLeNVVgOoXl3jmKXQT07IR1fYwPRIgiboTXU2tjiaAn3zpZ6cp8iaIvcTMxyrcwRR0P62w/0","discussTime":"2017-02-24"},{"id":258,"warmupPracticeId":185,"repliedId":null,"comment":"修改为啥不对？有些混淆修改与简化的区别了","openid":null,"addTime":1487915049000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"Jessie Wu\uD83C\uDF80\uD83D\uDC98","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/Q3auHgzwzM6nOlVFgMKicVRUia54mssmloGh0KvYD5Y5lt4wibRMMsZtUPpl2qCFFP8Htv3xUYf2kcUupGe8gjVqg/0","discussTime":"2017-02-24"}],"choice":null,"knowledge":{"id":57,"knowledge":"内容回顾 & 综合练习1","step":"复习","analysis":null,"means":null,"keynote":null,"pic":null,"audio":null,"appear":0,"example":null}}]},"code":200}
